# vimrc
#Â https://stackoverflow.com/questions/3776117/what-is-the-difference-between-the-remap-noremap-nnoremap-and-vnoremap-mapping
nmap : shortcut for normal mode
imap : shortcut for insert mode


#-----------------------------
# Neovim
# https://neovim.io/

# aptitude install neovim
$ nvim <file>
$ ln -s ~/.vim ~/.config/nvim
$ ln -s ~/.vimrc ~/.config/nvim/init.vim


???
Ctrl-] : visite a tag
Ctrl-T : back to previous
ctrl-o : go back
ctrl-i : go forward

